PrecisRe-appointment of Colette Savard, of Sillery, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour, for a term of five years; and designation of the said Colette Savard as an Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the said Board, effective September 1, 1993.
